{"tid":2139983,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[突發]美國加利福尼亞州範登堡空軍基地 發射了一枚 義勇兵III洲際彈道飛彈 目標不詳","createTime":"2020-08-04T15:52:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-04T22:51:21.000Z","uid":92476,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"ac18333f63a960d8d98e261ae9116021d3db962a","tid":2139983,"uid":92476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T15:52:02.000Z","msg":"2020年8月4日上午12:21 美國空軍試射了一枚民兵-3型洲際導彈。此次試射的導彈携帶3枚分導彈頭，從加州範登堡空軍基地發射，準確命中了南太平洋夸賈林環礁的預定目標。此次試射模擬了戰時環境，發射命令由E-6&ldquo;水星&rdquo;指揮機搭載的&ldquo;空基發射控制系統&rdquo;發出，驗證了美軍三位一體核打擊力量的戰場生存能力。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/LDv6hsVMJ88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLDv6hsVMJ88&d=dUSYmziiyXe0H9uVu%2B4Yd2zUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=446a460b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/LDv6hsVMJ88</a>"},{"pid":"1975df20ac60d4b12486ebfaeb937cbb393842c4","tid":2139983,"uid":92476,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T15:54:54.000Z","msg":"依個直播紐約 唔知點解勁多簡體字反共人士留言, 有時仲多過繁體字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e22a294228656f21ac0bb44601457662016a5d9","tid":2139983,"uid":55571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1975df20ac60d4b12486ebfaeb937cbb393842c4","tid":2139983,"uid":92476,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T15:54:54.000Z","msg":"依個直播紐約 唔知點解勁多簡體字反共人士留言, 有時仲多過繁體字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T15:57:51.000Z","msg":"唔想做目標五毛都要奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd9d1dbc006915d4459406604769fa0299b79e33","tid":2139983,"uid":284699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T15:59:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"916e07f8d96d6f0c07578b53a058a31d1dd2b884","tid":2139983,"uid":295230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T16:00:07.000Z","msg":"<strong>Minuteman III Test Launch Planned Early Tuesday from Vandenberg </strong><br />\n<br />\nAn unarmed Minuteman III missile is scheduled to pop out of an underground silo early Tuesday at Vandenberg Air Force Base, some 50 years after first joining the military's nuclear weapon arsenal.<br />\n<br />\nLiftoff of the three-stage weapon, carrying a mock warhead, is targeted for 12:21 a.m., with the six-hour launch window remaining open until 6:21 a.m. <br />\n<br />\nFor missile tests, the team typically shoots for a liftoff near the beginning of the launch window, but technical troubles or unfavorable weather at Vandenberg or downrange can delay departure.<br />\n<br />\nThe military will track the missile as it travels to a predetermined target approximately 4,200 miles away at the Kwajalein Atoll in the central Pacific Ocean.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;The purpose of the ICBM test launch program is to verify the safety, security, effectiveness and readiness of the weapon system,&rdquo; according to Air Force Global Strike Command."},{"pid":"019cafa74cc818721669feee122b882ca7f48071","tid":2139983,"uid":295230,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T16:03:11.000Z","msg":"義勇兵三型洲際彈道飛彈是美國核武庫唯一的陸基飛彈，由1970年開始服役到宜家已經開始老化，近年已經有現代化既計劃，無記錯前幾個月都有一次試射，屬於現代化計劃既一部分"},{"pid":"8fe5c20ec47c687454f9337fa1e082d41a7f088a","tid":2139983,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T16:03:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c776fed8e3ce2c4f6a7f6e4bf9afc9954e6a937","tid":2139983,"uid":117276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T16:1